==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unwish
<hw>Un*wish"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>wish</ets>.]</ety> <def>To wish not to be; to
destroy by wishing.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now thou hast <qex>unwished</qex> five thousand men.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unwist</ent>⟦br⟧
